snippet.title: Lifecraft Steam release trailer
snippet.description:
Lifecraft is coming on Steam 16 April 2024!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1839930/Lifecraft/

Survive and evolve as an organism in which you will literally start as a single cell and manage and organize all its functions to a fully fledged system! Assemble, breathe, eat, fight threats, produce energy, grow, anything is possible!
